ci.pi.es.i., muRaeyil paTiklum mANawarkaLuklu, aTutla kalwi ANTu mutal 10m wakuplu tErwu kiTaeyAtu.
 atEnEratlil, itE muRaeyae pin paRlumpaTi, mAnila kalwi wAriyangkaLae waRpuRutla mATlOm.
 10m wakuplu tErwae naTatluwatA, wENTAmA enpatae mAnila aracukaLtAn muTiwu ceyla wENTum, ena matliya amaeclar kapilcipal kURiyuLlAr.
 mERkut toTarcli malaeyil uRpatliyAkum pawAni ARu, kEraLA ellaekluL iruklum muklAli, pillUr aNae, mETluplALaeyam, ciRumukae, pawAni cAkar, catliyamangkalam wazhiyAka OTi, pawAniyil kAwiriyuTan kalakliRatu; itu waRlAta jIwanati.
 pillUr aNaeyiliruntu pawAni cAkar aNae warae pawAni ARu 60 ki.mI., tUram pAykiRatu.
 inta ARlil tEklampaTli, wanapatrakALiyamlan kOwil, mETluplALaeyam, ciRumukae Akiya iTangkaLil taniyAr AlaekaLin kazhiwu nIrum, mETluplALaeyam, kunlUr, ciRumukaeyil nakarin kazhiwu nIrum kalakliRatu.
 ANTu muzhuwatum toTarntu kalaklum kazhiwu nIrAl mAcupaTlu warum pawAni ARlu taNlIraetlAn kOwae, tiruplUr, IrOTu Akiya mUnRu mAwaTla maklaL kuTinIrAka payanpaTutlukinRanar.
 pawAni ARu mAcu paTuwatae taTukla naTawaTiklae eTukla wENTum, enRu pawAni natinIr maRlum nilatlaTi nIr pAtukAplu kuzhu aracuklu kOriklae wiTutluLlatu.


kOwae potuplaNitluRaeyin cuRluclUzhal kozhumam kOTlamum, pawAni nati nIr pAtukAplu kuzhuwum iNaentu, pawAni ARlil kazhiwu nIr kalaklum iTangkaLae camIpatlil nEril Aywu ceytana.
 kuzhu talaewar arangkacAmi, tuNaetlalaewar aruNkumAr, ceyalALar turaecAmi, poruLALar mInA harirAmalingkam, potuplaNitluRae utawi poRiyALarkaL mErilInA, centilkumAr AkiyOr pawAni ARlil kalaklum kazhiwu nIrae paricOtanaeklu eTutlanar.
